$5,000 TOWARDS CLOSING COSTS/BUY-DOWN RATE!!!  SELLER WELCOMES ALL OFFERS!!! 
This impressive house has an open concept that offers a harmonious blend of modern style and comfortable living. Boasting 3 bedrooms with walk-in closets, 2.5 baths, a 2-car bay, and a spacious versatile loft, this home encompasses a generous 2,088 sq. ft. Well-Equipped Kitchen with black appliances, matte black faucet, granite countertops, and ample cabinetry. Full sprinkler system. Step outside to a covered patio that extends your living space outdoors. This area is perfect for relaxing, dining, and enjoying the pleasant Texas weather. Situated in a prime location, this property grants quick access to shopping, dining, entertainment, and major highways, 15 minutes from ensuring a well-connected lifestyle
